&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Mission:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6sense&#39;s mission is to multiply what matters: growth, retention, and efficiency.&amp;nbsp; We envision a future where companies, teams and people reach their full potential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our People:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;People are the heart and soul of 6sense. We serve with passion and purpose. We live by our Being 6sense values of Win as One Team, Stay Curious, Do The Right Thing, Own the Outcome, and Create Belonging. &amp;nbsp;Every 6sensor plays a part in deﬁning the future of our industry-leading technology.&amp;nbsp; 6sense is a place where difference-makers roll up their sleeves, take risks, act with integrity, and measure success by the value we create for our customers.&amp;nbsp; We want 6sense to be the best chapter of your career.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a collaborative and results-oriented leader with 12+ years of experience in AdTech and Digital Campaign Operations, including at least 6 years in people management. You will lead a team responsible for delivering high-quality ABM, display, video, and programmatic campaigns across global markets while partnering with Client Success, Sales, Media Planning, Analytics, and Engineering.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What Will You Own&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, mentor, and develop a high-performing Campaign Operations team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end execution of ABM and digital advertising campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure campaigns meet KPIs, SLAs, pacing, and client expectations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor campaign health and resolve delivery issues through root cause analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive process improvements, automation, and operational excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical leadership on AdTech platforms and campaign implementation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage hiring, coaching, capacity planning, and performance management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare operational dashboards and leadership reports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current with AdTech trends, privacy regulations, and best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;12+ years in AdTech/Digital Campaign Operations with 6+ years leading teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing display, video, programmatic, and ABM campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on expertise with DSPs, SSPs, campaign trafficking, ad serving, audience targeting, pixel implementation, creative QA, and optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with The Trade Desk, DV360, Xandr, Beeswax, StackAdapt, CM360, or similar platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of HTML5 creatives, GA4, Microsoft Clarity, HubSpot, and attribution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced Microsoft Excel skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong leadership, stakeholder management, analytical, and communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Success in This Role Would Look Like&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and lead a high-performing campaign operations team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver campaigns that consistently achieve quality and performance goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve efficiency through automation and standardized processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the technical expert for campaign operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop strong cross-functional partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach and grow team members while driving continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
